# ShallowSearchResultDataA shallow search result of a patient/company address.## Properties| Key | string | An encrypted key value containing partial address information used to retrieve complete address details. || --- | --- | --- || Address | string | A single-line search result address. |## JSON Example```{"Key": "","Address": " 2 Paradise Street, Liverpool, Merseyside, L1 8JF"}```###
